name: 2023 The 10th International Conference on Artificial Intelligence
content: Publication: All papers will be strictly double blind reviewed by the program committee and reviewers, and accepted papers after proper registration and presentation will be published in one of the following Journals based on the topic of paper. Welcome you to submit the paper by Online Submission System. 1: International Journal of Mechanical Engineering and Robotics Research IJMERR, ISSN: 2278-0149 (Online) Abstracting/Indexing: Scopus, CNKI, Google Scholar, Crossref, etc. 2: International Journal of Machine Learning IJML, ISSN: 2972-368X Abstracting/Indexing: Inspec (IET), Google Scholar, Crossref, ProQuest, Electronic Journals Library, CNKI.
